    <chapter xml:id="elemdef-opf-meta-overview">
        <title>Overview</title>

        <section xml:id="sec-purpose-scope" conformance="informative">
            <title>Purpose and Scope</title>
            <para> This vocabulary, a part of EPUBÂ® 3, defines a set of properties for describing various features of the
                    <olink targetdoc="packages" targetptr="sec-package-doc" type="epub-spec"/>.</para>
            <para>The properties in this vocabulary are usable in the various Package Document attributes that accept the
                    <olink targetdoc="packages" targetptr="sec-property-datatype" type="epub-spec">property datatype</olink>,
                and are grouped by the element and attribute that they can be used in.</para>
            <para>This vocabulary is a companion to the <xref linkend="refPackages3"/> specification and is intended to be
                read in conjunction with that document.</para>
        </section>

        <section xml:id="sec-ref">
            <title>Referencing</title>

            <para>Properties without a prefix are referenceable using the base IRI
                    <uri>http://idpf.org/epub/vocab/package/#</uri>.</para>
        </section>

